<h2 id="2-circle-the-wagons">2. Circle the Wagons</h2>

<p>The “tail” (the last element) of your LinkedList doesn’t have a <code class="highlighter-rouge">next_node</code>. Rewrite your functionality so that the <code class="highlighter-rouge">next_node</code> of the “tail” now points to the head, but all other functionality still works.</p>
:ET